at you now?

563
00:48:56,255 --> 00:48:58,519
Getting old?

564
00:48:58,558 --> 00:49:01,220
- Dying?
- Hell no.

565
00:49:02,495 --> 00:49:05,430
- What then?
- Being useless.

566
00:49:05,464 --> 00:49:07,932
When we were young
there was always a reason,

567
00:49:07,967 --> 00:49:10,231
