brother.

571
00:49:29,388 --> 00:49:31,822
- Go get some beers.
- All right.

572
00:49:31,858 --> 00:49:34,850
Hey, old man,

573
00:49:34,894 --> 00:49:36,919
how's that barbecue?

574
00:49:36,963 --> 00:49:39,397
Give me some.

575
00:49:39,432 --> 00:49:42,868
