of what l've been talking about.

578
00:49:50,042 --> 00:49:52,476
Since this boy was suckling on
his momma's tit,

579
00:49:52,511 --> 00:49:54,672
he's been given
everything but discipline.

580
00:49:54,714 --> 00:49:56,773
And now his idea
of courage and manhood

581
